According to the status on the screen, we can see the tab of Firefox browser, which contains the search results of "Today in History". Our plan is to click a result, so we need to perform the following operations:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 408, "height": 342}}
]
```Note that the coordinates here are relative to the top left corner of the screen. After performing this operation, you will select the search results of "Today in History" and open the corresponding webpage.
